# App Router

- `page.tsx` / `layout.tsx`: **sem lógica** — importar de `widgets/` ou `features/`
- Providers globais: `app/providers/`
- `app/api/**/route.ts`: validar Zod → chamar `shared/api` ou `features/*/api`
- Server Actions: `"use server"`; delegar para `features/*/api`

Next 16: proxy em `src/proxy.ts` (não `middleware.ts`).

Skills: `next-core` · `next-api` · `next-proxy`
